---
/**
 * ai-agents · 0005 · Figure 2 — goal → planner → plan (subtasks) → execute, with
 * a re-plan feedback loop. Verbatim from the source HTML. Marker refs resolve
 * against the shared <defs> SVG emitted once at the top of the lesson body.
 */
---

<figure>
    <svg
        viewBox="0 0 620 244"
        role="img"
        aria-label="A goal flows into a planner that decomposes it into ordered subtasks, which feed execution, with a re-plan feedback loop"
    >
        <g font-family="ui-sans-serif,system-ui,sans-serif">
            <!-- GOAL -->
            <rect x="12" y="104" width="84" height="44" rx="8" fill="#fff" stroke="#d8d4c8"></rect>
            <text
                x="54"
                y="123"
                text-anchor="middle"
                font-size="11"
                font-weight="700"
                fill="#111110">Goal</text
            >
            <text x="54" y="138" text-anchor="middle" font-size="8.5" fill="#6b675f"
                >"fix the bug"</text
            >
            <line
                x1="96"
                y1="126"
                x2="120"
                y2="126"
                stroke="#6b675f"
                stroke-width="1.5"
                marker-end="url(#arw)"></line>
            <!-- PLANNER -->
            <rect
                x="122"
                y="102"
                width="104"
                height="48"
                rx="8"
                fill="#f1eee2"
                stroke="#7a1f12"
                stroke-width="1.4"></rect>
            <text
                x="174"
                y="121"
                text-anchor="middle"
                font-size="11"
                font-weight="700"
                fill="#7a1f12">Planner (LLM)</text
            >
            <text x="174" y="137" text-anchor="middle" font-size="8.5" fill="#6b675f"
                >decompose + order</text
            >
            <line
                x1="226"
                y1="120"
                x2="260"
                y2="40"
                stroke="#6b675f"
                stroke-width="1.5"
                marker-end="url(#arw)"></line>
            <!-- PLAN header -->
            <rect x="262" y="16" width="120" height="28" rx="7" fill="#ede9f7" stroke="#5b54e6"
            ></rect>
            <text
                x="322"
                y="34"
                text-anchor="middle"
                font-size="10.5"
                font-weight="700"
                fill="#5b54e6">PLAN (subtasks)</text
            >
            <!-- spine -->
            <line x1="270" y1="44" x2="270" y2="206" stroke="#bdb8d8" stroke-width="1.3"></line>
            <!-- subtasks -->
            <rect x="284" y="56" width="128" height="28" rx="6" fill="#fff" stroke="#d8d4c8"
            ></rect><text x="348" y="74" text-anchor="middle" font-size="9.5" fill="#111110"
                >S1 · reproduce</text
            >
            <rect x="284" y="98" width="128" height="28" rx="6" fill="#fff" stroke="#d8d4c8"
            ></rect><text x="348" y="116" text-anchor="middle" font-size="9.5" fill="#111110"
                >S2 · locate cause</text
            >
            <rect x="284" y="140" width="128" height="28" rx="6" fill="#fff" stroke="#d8d4c8"
            ></rect><text x="348" y="158" text-anchor="middle" font-size="9.5" fill="#111110"
                >S3 · patch</text
            >
            <rect x="284" y="182" width="128" height="28" rx="6" fill="#fff" stroke="#d8d4c8"
            ></rect><text x="348" y="200" text-anchor="middle" font-size="9.5" fill="#111110"
                >S4 · add test</text
            >
            <line x1="270" y1="70" x2="284" y2="70" stroke="#bdb8d8" stroke-width="1.3"></line>
            <line x1="270" y1="112" x2="284" y2="112" stroke="#bdb8d8" stroke-width="1.3"></line>
            <line x1="270" y1="154" x2="284" y2="154" stroke="#bdb8d8" stroke-width="1.3"></line>
            <line x1="270" y1="196" x2="284" y2="196" stroke="#bdb8d8" stroke-width="1.3"></line>
            <!-- to EXECUTE -->
            <line
                x1="412"
                y1="70"
                x2="452"
                y2="118"
                stroke="#7a1f12"
                stroke-width="1.2"
                marker-end="url(#arwA)"></line>
            <line
                x1="412"
                y1="112"
                x2="452"
                y2="122"
                stroke="#7a1f12"
                stroke-width="1.2"
                marker-end="url(#arwA)"></line>
            <line
                x1="412"
                y1="154"
                x2="452"
                y2="128"
                stroke="#7a1f12"
                stroke-width="1.2"
                marker-end="url(#arwA)"></line>
            <line
                x1="412"
                y1="196"
                x2="452"
                y2="132"
                stroke="#7a1f12"
                stroke-width="1.2"
                marker-end="url(#arwA)"></line>
            <!-- EXECUTE -->
            <rect
                x="454"
                y="104"
                width="96"
                height="44"
                rx="8"
                fill="#eef5ee"
                stroke="#2f5d3a"
                stroke-width="1.4"></rect>
            <text
                x="502"
                y="123"
                text-anchor="middle"
                font-size="11"
                font-weight="700"
                fill="#2f5d3a">Execute</text
            >
            <text x="502" y="138" text-anchor="middle" font-size="8.5" fill="#2f5d3a"
                >one step at a time</text
            >
            <!-- re-plan feedback -->
            <path
                d="M502,148 L502,224 L174,224 L174,150"
                fill="none"
                stroke="#9a2417"
                stroke-width="1.4"
                stroke-dasharray="5 3"
                marker-end="url(#arwR)"></path>
            <text
                x="338"
                y="239"
                text-anchor="middle"
                font-size="9.5"
                font-weight="600"
                fill="#9a2417"
                >&#8635; re-plan: when reality diverges, replace the remaining steps</text
            >
        </g>
    </svg>
    <figcaption>
        The plan is a hypothesis, not a contract. Execution feeds reality back; the planner revises
        the <em>unstarted</em> steps. A plan with no re-plan path is a brittle script.
    </figcaption>
</figure>
